                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "sorting-whites",
            "title": "Sorting by color: whites",
            "type": "content",
            "description": "Sorting whites is all about keeping your light-colored clothes looking bright and fresh. By separating whites from colors, you’ll prevent dye transfer and keep your whites looking their best. Whites typically include white shirts, socks, undergarments, and white sheets. They can often be washed with pastels.",
            "images": [
                {
                    "src": "imgs/whites.png",
                    "alt": "Sorting whites"
