            "type": "lesson",
            "next_page": "mainpage3",
            "description": "Choosing the right wash settings is crucial for keeping your clothes looking their best. By selecting the appropriate cycle, temperature, and spin speed, you’ll ensure that your clothes are cleaned effectively without causing damage.",
